 in the message.</i>

00:12:40.125 --> 00:12:43.428
[man] Is there a difference
in time between any of these?

00:12:43.461 --> 00:12:45.564
[woman]
It doesn't look like it.
The rhythm doesn't vary.

00:12:45.597 --> 00:12:46.798
[man]
It doesn't vary?

