-Here it is.
-Thank you.

00:14:25.497 --> 00:14:28.133
-All right, we will continue.
-All right, I'll leave
you guys to it.

00:14:28.166 --> 00:14:29.668
[man]
Okay, this is pretty long here.

00:14:29.701 --> 00:14:31.270
[woman]
It's not repeating at all.

00:14:31.303 --> 00:14:32.638 size:63% position:31%
Does it look like
an even distribution

00:14:32.671 --> 00:14:34.106 align:start position:0%
of zeros and ones?

